cards.content: {"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"heading","attrs":{"id":"e7d73236-9bed-4a3c-a092-29a65d3e1354","level":1},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"为什么是Haze？"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"5113b3d6-4bac-4c5b-aa7e-cb3e30b38217"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Haze源于我的名字：haozhe中字母组成的单词，其意迷蒙，很符合我当时的心境，作为一个普通人，平凡地在迷蒙中找寻自己的方向，为了寻找这个方向不断地"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"color","attrs":{"type":"text","color":"red"}}],"text":"求知"},{"type":"text","text":"、"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"color","attrs":{"type":"text","color":"red"}}],"text":"努力"},{"type":"text","text":"、"},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"color","attrs":{"type":"text","color":"red"}}],"text":"自驱"},{"type":"text","text":"。这几个词意很好的囊括了我目前的一生，因而获名。"}]},{"type":"image","attrs":{"id":"6d6c3906-116e-4534-aabc-247d42a02685","src":"https://media.heptabase.com/v1/images/6a02ed7f-376a-4e01-a43d-3c503d5eebcc/e6645adf-3dc0-4f3b-bc0f-f95f6b46c56e/image.png#center","fileId":null,"alt":null,"title":null,"width":"40%","alignment":"center"}},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"f3f7a470-f97f-4026-add1-da4f84b6ba60"},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"🤣而188来源于我的身高，并非为了炫耀，无它，唯暴富梦尔，希望谐音“要发发”给我带来财运。"}]},{"type":"paragraph","attrs":{"id":"05f53755-8f63-4a81-ab16-f4db6c311f26"}}]}
